Wow! Just a casual Friday in the NFL, huh? That's the way we were trending until multiple blockbusters took place involvingÂ the 49ers, Dolphins and Eagles and collection of top draft picks. Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and Josh Edwards to break down the moves. What is San Fran's focus moving inside the Top 3 and which quarterback could they end up with? The guys also evaluate how Miami fared, ultimately ending up with the 6th pick in 2021 and why Philly decided to move back.Â The guys also hit on the implications for the rest of the NFL and the rest of the 1st round.
